Coerce to an mcarray object

as.mcarray.Rd

Coerces MCMC objects to an mcarray.object.

as.mcarray(x, ...)

# S3 method for mcmcarray
as.mcarray(x, ...)

Arguments

x

object to coerce.
...

Unused.

Methods (by class)

  • mcmcarray: Coerces mcmcarray object to an mcarray object

Examples

as.mcarray(mcmcr_example$beta)
